	  (cob_get_temp_file) to (cob_get_sort_tempfile)
	* fileio.c (cob_srttmpfile): using new (cob_temp_name) to get the name
	* common.c: use (cob_sys_getpid) everywhere instead of (getpid);
	  use (setenv) if available

